text: Brook Toland is an American actress best known for her role on ABC Family's Becoming Us television show, which was produced by Ryan Seacrest. Prior to this, Toland co-starred in an independent film called Innocent in 2009 with Alexa Vega. ==Filmography== ===Film & Television=== {| class="wikitable sortable" ! Year ! Title !
